title: Eifert's jersey a top-seller at Bengals Pro Shop
text:
Eifert's jersey a top-seller at Bengals Pro Shop 
By Eric Dutkiewicz - 21Alive October 15, 2015 Updated Oct 15, 2015 at 12:29 AM EDT 
CINCINNATI (21Alive) - Tyler Eifert's breakout season for the Cincinnati Bengals has reportedly made his jersey the most popular at the Bengals Pro Shop. 
Eifert's No. 85 is the top-selling Bengals uniform at the Bengals Pro Shop at Paul Brown Stadium as well as online Pro Shop sales, according to the Cincinnati Business Courier . 
Digital Daily – subscribe to our daily newsletter 
Wide receiver A.J. Green's No. 18 is second and quarterback Andy Dalton's No. 14 is third most popular among Bengals jerseys. 
The rankings reflect jersey sales since Aug. 1, Bengals merchandise manager Monty Montague says in the article. He would not tell the publication specific sales numbers.
